			I would like to add that the EXP for this quest is pretty good for characters under level 10. The belts are easy to come by, and at 9 I was able to turn in 12 of them to complete my last bubble of EXP to reach level 10. Every belt can gain a gold piece of so of additional loot, so unless you are level 13 or above, it is almost foolish NOT to do this quest if you spend any appreciable amount of time in Crushbone.
